[32m│[0m - All requests used `username=test&password=test`                                                                                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Decoded all resulting session cookies to verify user_id value                                                                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Accessed dashboard with each session to verify which user was logged in                                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                                                                                   [32m│[0m
